:"The Bee","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":1967,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1967.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/1967.mp3"],"text":"وَإِنَّ لَكُمْ فِى ٱلْأَنْعَٰمِ لَعِبْرَةًۭ ۖ نُّسْقِيكُم مِّمَّا فِى بُطُونِهِۦ مِنۢ بَيْنِ فَرْثٍۢ وَدَمٍۢ لَّبَنًا خَالِصًۭا سَآئِغًۭا لِّلشَّٰرِبِينَ","numberInSurah":66,"juz":14,"manzil":3,"page":274,"ruku":232,"hizbQuarter":109,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":16,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّحۡلِ","englishName":"An-Nahl","englishNameTranslation":"The Bee","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":1968,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1968.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/1968.mp3"],"text":"وَمِن ثَمَرَٰتِ ٱلنَّخِيلِ وَٱلْأَعْنَٰبِ تَتَّخِذُونَ مِنْهُ سَكَرًۭا وَرِزْقًا حَسَنًا ۗ إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَءَايَةًۭ لِّقَوْمٍۢ يَعْقِلُونَ","numberInSurah":67,"juz":14,"manzil":3,"page":274,"ruku":232,"hizbQuarter":109,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":16,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّحۡلِ","englishName":"An-Nahl","englishNameTranslation":"The Bee","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":1969,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1969.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/1969.mp3"],"text":"وَأَوْحَىٰ رَبُّكَ إِلَى ٱلنَّحْلِ أَنِ ٱتَّخِذِى مِنَ ٱلْجِبَالِ بُيُوتًۭا وَمِنَ ٱلشَّجَرِ وَمِمَّا يَعْرِشُونَ","numberInSurah":68,"juz":14,"manzil":3,"page":274,"ruku":232,"hizbQuarter":109,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":16,"name":"سُورَةُ النَّحۡلِ","englishName":"An-Nahl","englishNameTranslation":"The Bee","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":1970,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1970.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/1970.mp3"],"text":"ثُمَّ كُلِى مِن كُلِّ ٱلثَّمَرَٰتِ فَٱسْلُكِى سُبُلَ رَبِّكِ ذُلُلًۭا ۚ يَخْرُجُ مِنۢ بُطُونِهَا شَرَابٌۭ مُّخْتَلِفٌ أَلْوَٰنُهُۥ فِيهِ ش